<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pat" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pat,</orth> quite to the purpose, fitly, exactly: <cit><quote>are we all met? p. p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 3.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. III, 1, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it will fall p. as I told you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 5.188.2" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 188</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>nor could come p. betwixt too early and too late,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 2.3.84" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 3, 84</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>now might I do it p.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.3.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 3, 73</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and p. he comes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.2.146" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 2, 146</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>